---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="The Patient Journey">
  <section class="py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-[var(--primary-text)] mb-4">Your Path to a Renewed You</h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[var(--primary-text)] max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        We believe in a transparent, supportive, and collaborative process. Here is what you can expect on your journey with us.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pb-20 md:pb-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="relative">
        <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute left-1/2 top-0 h-full w-px bg-gray-200 hidden md:block"></div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 md:gap-20 items-start">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-end">
            <div class="md:text-right max-w-md">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-end gap-4 mb-4">
                <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary-text)]">Your Comprehensive Consultation</h3>
                <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent-green)] text-white text-xl font-bold">1</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-[var(--primary-text)]/80 mb-6">
                Your journey begins with a private, in-depth consultation with our physician. We take the time to listen to your story, understand your goals, and conduct a thorough health assessment.
              </p>
              <div class="aspect-w-4 aspect-h-3 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
                <img alt="A serene consultation room with a doctor and a patient." class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDGwzcrdBYHavDD1bcvtEsfdHOkoCsWXhhhWL4WS58g-XbDN5-4CdUxnCLTmbRRJyFVwmX9D9afDmbKz3Rx1OaniL2EvNQS4-UXjk0vnzJlOEgdyvTNvp97a6eOQdXAE8ikjUujH2k1GbblYy9sAHaKIYl6QKB9WwczIvPTbozLp3qYuTQpGnq_aJMU1Fjr9bPXFOyIZ1rpVYs2kwekgokr38WVvRxPWqRpqLzViFSD2eh6P9rRWnlF89AElwrQylUsF-LXnxoS_UHE"/>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden md:block"></div>

          <div class="hidden md:block"></div>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start">
            <div class="max-w-md">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-4 mb-4">
                <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent-blue)] text-white text-xl font-bold">2</span>
                <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary-text)]">Your Personalized Plan</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-[var(--primary-text)]/80 mb-6">
                Using the insights from your consultation, our medical team designs a personalized treatment plan just for you.
              </p>
              <div class="aspect-w-4 aspect-h-3 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
                <img alt="A doctor reviewing a personalized plan on a tablet." class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBR6LwFnRPrwADhVUIqZfxp9CIvaF8vN5ePFCpiqCBjUdDSqzj1zxeyJb-fifr9mgiG2uPCFHioHHtvpN945FJfeK-skRQBzGS4tKt70JxwGkASoe8-J1SnWAIKUyBC0gVfpT6dlXsJf3bkFpnE3RotiEabi5PzailTvBhlG__XvGcUw58ytsFkkJEGRWM-onW1eRx1FVspOuVIyCJp0QHsyXwgh-35UHhSSUmDVIoHV0IXrbYrwoXUmvPyinNixvbknHgvB7FE_fTN"/>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-end">
            <div class="md:text-right max-w-md">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-end gap-4 mb-4">
                <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary-text)]">Ongoing Physician Guidance & Support</h3>
                <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent-gold)] text-white text-xl font-bold">3</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-[var(--primary-text)]/80 mb-6">
                You will have regular follow-up appointments with our team to monitor your results, make any necessary adjustments, and provide the guidance you need to succeed.
              </p>
              <div class="aspect-w-4 aspect-h-3 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
                <img alt="A supportive doctor listening to a patient in a comfortable setting." class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCCkQCrhZzB_35qFTIRzqUd8xnOlOm-W0hnkZ6EFweVvt9nPSp942wCoBUD6aNYgR_A14W5edq2n5q7elmpYAr3JWU1BebU59cesGs00qYxXTbO6K5PUI7Eu7dYmTwOEOXRFSY0DSJewIwIggYwWujfmC8umMDUhXlXw8VedtUd1wnNJg7Ab9kZVa15mITGzwnHKNND-as-7vsDlnCDqV7ZVnrdq8TDsbv7s8XlPvOmaNjTu02w01lab9mr_dpz95nf-lOkRl08J0bc"/>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden md:block"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>